BT
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (ABSTRACT) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 706 Td (Raitha-Varta is a full-stack Android application designed for farmers. Agricultural) Tj
72 691 Td (advisories are often published as long PDF files or text messages, which may be) Tj
72 676 Td (difficult for farmers to read quickly in the field. The proposed application converts) Tj
72 661 Td (advisory information into short flash-card tips that are easy to understand and act) Tj
72 646 Td (upon.) Tj
72 623 Td (The Android app displays crop-specific daily tips, supports offline storage using Room) Tj
72 608 Td (Database, and allows farmers to submit crop or leaf problems with a selected leaf) Tj
72 593 Td (photo. A Node.js backend provides REST API support, stores expert requests, and) Tj
72 578 Td (returns advisory outcomes in Kannada and English. A browser-based Expert Dashboard) Tj
72 563 Td (allows experts to review farmer requests and update bilingual responses.) Tj
72 540 Td (The project focuses on digital inclusion, precision farming, and fast access to) Tj
72 525 Td (scientifically guided crop advisory information.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
