BT
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (1. INTRODUCTION) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 706 Td (Agriculture is one of the most important sectors in India. Farmers require timely and) Tj
72 691 Td (reliable information about crop care, pest control, weather-based action, and disease) Tj
72 676 Td (prevention. Many advisory systems provide useful information, but the content is often) Tj
72 661 Td (lengthy and not suitable for quick field usage.) Tj
72 638 Td (Raitha-Varta addresses this issue by presenting farming advisories as short, swipeable) Tj
72 623 Td (flash cards. The application is designed to be simple, high-contrast, and useful for) Tj
72 608 Td (farmers. It supports Kannada and English guidance and provides an Expert Ask feature) Tj
72 593 Td (for leaf-photo based advisory support.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
18 0 obj
<< /Type /Page /Parent 2 0 R /MediaBox [0 0 612 792] /Resources << /Font << /F1 3 0 R >> >> /Contents 19 0 R >>
endobj
19 0 obj
<< /Length 578 >>
stream
BT
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (2. PROBLEM STATEMENT) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 706 Td (Agricultural experts and Krishi Vigyana Kendras release crop advisories every week.) Tj
72 691 Td (These advisories may be long PDF files or text messages. Farmers need short,) Tj
72 676 Td (actionable tips that are specific to their crop and district.) Tj
72 653 Td (The project problem is to create an Android application that converts complex) Tj
72 638 Td (agricultural information into daily one-minute tips and provides a backend-supported) Tj
72 623 Td (expert consultation feature.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
20 0 obj
<< /Type /Page /Parent 2 0 R /MediaBox [0 0 612 792] /Resources << /Font << /F1 3 0 R >> >> /Contents 21 0 R >>
endobj
