<< /Length 688 >>
stream
BT
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (3. OBJECTIVES) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 706 Td (To develop a Kotlin-based Android app for farmers.) Tj
72 683 Td (To display daily crop advisory tips using swipeable flash cards.) Tj
72 660 Td (To provide crop category filters such as Paddy, Arecanut, Coconut, and Tomato.) Tj
72 637 Td (To store tips offline using Room Database.) Tj
72 614 Td (To connect the app with a backend REST API using Retrofit.) Tj
72 591 Td (To allow farmers to submit leaf-photo based Expert Ask requests.) Tj
72 568 Td (To provide expert outcomes in Kannada and English.) Tj
72 545 Td (To create a browser-based Expert Dashboard for reviewing and updating farmer requests.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
