BT
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (10. RESULTS AND OUTCOMES) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 706 Td (The project successfully implements a farmer-facing Android application and) Tj
72 691 Td (backend-supported advisory system. The app displays daily advisory cards, stores data) Tj
72 676 Td (offline, and supports expert consultation through a backend API.) Tj
72 653 Td (The Expert Dashboard improves the project by allowing experts to review submitted) Tj
72 638 Td (requests and update outcomes in Kannada and English. This makes the system more) Tj
72 623 Td (complete and closer to a real agriculture advisory platform.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
