BT
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (11. ADVANTAGES) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 706 Td (Simple and farmer-friendly interface.) Tj
72 683 Td (Short actionable crop tips instead of long advisory documents.) Tj
72 660 Td (Kannada and English support for wider accessibility.) Tj
72 637 Td (Offline tip viewing through Room Database.) Tj
72 614 Td (Backend API support for real-time updates.) Tj
72 591 Td (Expert Dashboard for advisory management.) Tj
72 568 Td (Persistent JSON storage for submitted expert requests.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
