BT
/F1 18 Tf
72 742 Td (12. LIMITATIONS) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 706 Td (The leaf photo is represented using a device URI for demo purposes and is not yet) Tj
72 691 Td (uploaded as an actual image file to the backend.) Tj
72 668 Td (The expert advice is partly simulated and requires real agriculture expert validation) Tj
72 653 Td (for production use.) Tj
72 630 Td (The backend uses JSON file storage, which is suitable for demos but not ideal for) Tj
72 615 Td (large-scale deployment.) Tj
72 592 Td (Authentication is not implemented for the Expert Dashboard.) Tj
ET

endstream
endobj
