72 742 Td (14. CONCLUSION) Tj
/F1 11 Tf
72 706 Td (Raitha-Varta is a useful agriculture advisory application that combines Android) Tj
72 691 Td (development, offline local storage, backend APIs, and an Expert Dashboard. The project) Tj
72 676 Td (demonstrates how digital tools can simplify agricultural information and support) Tj
72 661 Td (farmers with quick, bilingual advisory outcomes.) Tj
72 638 Td (The system meets the major goals of the project: short daily tips, crop filtering,) Tj
72 623 Td (Kannada and English information, offline viewing, expert consultation, and) Tj
72 608 Td (backend-supported advisory management.) Tj
